name: Public access to procurement information
text: §103D-105  Public access to procurement information.  Government records relating to procurement shall be available to the public as provided in chapter 92F.  Part I of chapter 92 shall not apply to discussions, deliberations, or decisions required to be conducted or made confidentially under this chapter. [L Sp 1993, c 8, pt of §2; am L 1995, c 178, §4]
